{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"static","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"let","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"firstLine","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"VerticalAlignment","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:7SwiftUI17VerticalAlignmentV"}]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This alignment is analogous to the default behavior of SwiftUI’s "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Label"},{"type":"text","text":", where"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the icon is vertically centered with the first line of the label text. Unlike"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Label"},{"type":"text","text":", this alignment can be used with any view, any spacing, and any number"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"of subviews."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The alignment uses SwiftUI’s text baseline alignment guides to calculate the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"center of the first line. It works by finding the difference between the first"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"and last text baselines, then computing the midpoint of the remaining height."}]},{"level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Usage","anchor":"Usage"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Use "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":".firstLine"},{"type":"text","text":" as the alignment parameter for "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"HStack"},{"type":"text","text":":"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["HStack(alignment: .firstLine, spacing: 12) {","  Image(systemName: \"star.fill\")","    .foregroundStyle(.yellow)","  VStack(alignment: .leading) {","    Text(\"First Line\")","      .font(.headline)","    Text(\"Second Line\")","    Text(\"Third Line\")","  }","}"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The star icon will be vertically centered with “First Line”, regardless of how"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"many additional lines of text appear below."}]},{"level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Common Use Cases","anchor":"Common-Use-Cases"},{"items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Timeline entries","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":": Align node indicators with the first line of event descriptions","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"List items","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":": Align icons or checkboxes with the first line of multiline labels","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Form fields","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":": Align validation icons with the first line of error messages","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Comments\/Reviews","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":": Align avatars with the first line of comment text","type":"text"}]}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"level":2,"type":"heading","text":"How It Works","anchor":"How-It-Works"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The alignment calculates:"}]},{"items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The height after the first line: ","type":"text"},{"code":"lastTextBaseline - firstTextBaseline","type":"codeVoice"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The height of the first line: ","type":"text"},{"code":"totalHeight - heightAfterFirstLine","type":"codeVoice"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The center point: ","type":"text"},{"code":"heightOfFirstLine \/ 2","type":"codeVoice"}]}]}],"type":"orderedList"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This positions the alignment guide at the vertical center of the first line of text."}]}]}],"metadata":{"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"static"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"let"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"firstLine"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"VerticalAlignment","preciseIdentifier":"s:7SwiftUI17VerticalAlignmentV"}],"modules":[{"relatedModules":["SwiftUICore"],"name":"IronCore"}],"roleHeading":"Type Property","extendedModule":"SwiftUICore","title":"firstLine","symbolKind":"property","role":"symbol","externalID":"s:7SwiftUI17VerticalAlignmentV8IronCoreE9firstLineACvpZ"},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/IronCore\/documentation\/IronCore\/SwiftUICore\/VerticalAlignment\/firstLine"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/IronCore\/documentation\/IronCore","doc:\/\/IronCore\/documentation\/IronCore\/SwiftUICore","doc:\/\/IronCore\/documentation\/IronCore\/SwiftUICore\/VerticalAlignment"]]},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/ironcore\/swiftuicore\/verticalalignment\/firstline"]}],"sections":[],"kind":"symbol","schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"minor":3,"major":0},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Aligns content to the center of the first line of text."}],"references":{"doc://IronCore/documentation/IronCore/SwiftUICore":{"type":"topic","title":"SwiftUICore","url":"\/documentation\/ironcore\/swiftuicore","kind":"symbol","role":"collection","identifier":"doc:\/\/IronCore\/documentation\/IronCore\/SwiftUICore","abstract":[]},"doc://IronCore/documentation/IronCore/SwiftUICore/VerticalAlignment":{"type":"topic","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"extension"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"VerticalAlignment","preciseIdentifier":"s:7SwiftUI17VerticalAlignmentV"}],"title":"VerticalAlignment","kind":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"VerticalAlignment"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Provides first-line text alignment for use in HStack layouts."}],"url":"\/documentation\/ironcore\/swiftuicore\/verticalalignment","identifier":"doc:\/\/IronCore\/documentation\/IronCore\/SwiftUICore\/VerticalAlignment","role":"symbol"},"doc://IronCore/documentation/IronCore/SwiftUICore/VerticalAlignment/firstLine":{"url":"\/documentation\/ironcore\/swiftuicore\/verticalalignment\/firstline","type":"topic","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Aligns content to the center of the first line of text."}],"role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/IronCore\/documentation\/IronCore\/SwiftUICore\/VerticalAlignment\/firstLine","title":"firstLine","fragments":[{"text":"static","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"let","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"firstLine","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:7SwiftUI17VerticalAlignmentV","text":"VerticalAlignment","kind":"typeIdentifier"}]},"doc://IronCore/documentation/IronCore":{"type":"topic","abstract":[{"text":"Foundation module providing theming, tokens, and accessibility utilities.","type":"text"}],"url":"\/documentation\/ironcore","title":"IronCore","identifier":"doc:\/\/IronCore\/documentation\/IronCore","kind":"symbol","role":"collection"}}}